    • Constructor Detail

      • SelectProjectJoinQuery

        public SelectProjectJoinQuery(Function head,
                              List<Function> body)
        Given a mappings in currentMapping, this method will return a new mappings in which no constants appear in the body of database predicates. This is done by replacing the constant occurrence with a fresh variable, and adding a new equality condition to the body of the mapping.

        For example, let the mapping m be

        A(x) :- T(x,y,22)

        Then this method will replace m by the mapping m'

        A(x) :- T(x,y,z), EQ(z,22)
